Available Tools: get_instance_status | list_instances | get_instance_metrics
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "instance_id": "string", "region": "string", "filter": "string" }
Response Schema: { "instances": [{ "id": "string", "type": "string", "state": "string", "ip": "string" }] }
---
Question: What are the real-time CPU and RAM figures for instance i-1122334455 in af-south-1?
Call: { "func_call": "get_instance_metrics", "instance_id": "i-1122334455", "region": "af-south-1", "filter": "cpu,memory" }
Response: { "instances": [{ "id": "i-1122334455", "type": "m5.2xlarge", "state": "running", "ip": "10.50.60.70" }] }

Question: Show me disk I/O and CPU load for storage-node-alpha in eu-west-3.
Call: { "func_call": "get_instance_metrics", "instance_id": "storage-node-alpha", "region": "eu-west-3", "filter": "disk,cpu" }
Response: { "instances": [{ "id": "storage-node-alpha", "type": "i3.xlarge", "state": "running", "ip": "172.18.22.11" }] }

